=====Usage notes=====
* Normally, the subject of {{lang|zh|殺}} should be [[animate]]. The sentence "A tiger killed many people." can be validly translated as {{lang|zh|老虎殺死數人}}, while the sentence "This accident killed many people." is seldom translated as *{{lang|zh|這次事故殺死數人}}. For death caused by non-living things, split forms of {{zh-l|致死}} are often used instead:
*: {{zh-x|這 次 事故 '''致''' 數 人 '''死亡'''。|This accident '''caused''' many people's '''deaths'''.}}

